    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>&quot;Eeny, meeny, miney, moe</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Creepy GREEN EYES are on the wall.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Don't you think all this is joke,</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Little girl is gonna choke!&quot;</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293610/extras/76c6c9bcba41c7bd9526e8332c2dfcb1.poster.avif?t=1740394142\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293610/extras/76c6c9bcba41c7bd9526e8332c2dfcb1.webm?t=1740394142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293610/extras/76c6c9bcba41c7bd9526e8332c2dfcb1.mp4?t=1740394142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever heard of the cursed Green Vinyl? Or perhaps the Black Blanket is trying to kill you at night? Have you ever encountered a Blue Finger  in a bun? The visual novel &quot;SOVIET SPOOKY TALES: Green Eyes&quot; is the first of five planned games set in the lore of Soviet children's spooky stories, where everything is real. The story follows a girl named Dasha from class 4th &quot;B,&quot; who disobeyed her mother and listened to the green record. Along with her, you will confront a mysterious and terrifying evil, and it is up to you to decide what awaits her in the end. ^___^</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293610/extras/50173a1c61fe4dba79a61698d3141af8.poster.avif?t=1740394142\" width=600 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293610/extras/50173a1c61fe4dba79a61698d3141af8.webm?t=1740394142\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3293610/extras/50173a1c61fe4dba79a61698d3141af8.mp4?t=1740394142\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GAME FEATURES:</strong>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Immerse yourself in the Soviet era of 1986 during the &quot;Perestroika,&quot; five years before the fall of the USSR </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● The game features warm and cozy pixel art graphics </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Animated characters and cutscenes </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Three endings: CORPSE, COWARD, and COMRADE </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● You can eat a lucky ticket </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● There is a grandma with borscht </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >● Total gameplay time is approximately 3.5 hours</p>",
